---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact Us
description: Get your free ERC case review. Our team responds within 24 hours. Everything you share is confidential.
---
<!-- Hero -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 10rem; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #ffffff 100%);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
            <span class="section-tag">Contact Us</span>
            <h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: 3rem;">Get Your Free Case Review</h1>
            <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto" style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Our team responds within 24 hours. Everything you share is confidential.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact Options -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div style="display: grid; gap: 4rem;" class="hero-grid">
            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <div id="contact-form">
                <div class="lead-form-card" style="max-width: none;">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Request Your Free Assessment</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Fill out the form below and we'll contact you within 24 hours.</p>

                    <form data-lead-form>
                        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <input type="text" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name *" required class="form-input">
                            <input type="text" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name *" required class="form-input">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Business Email *" required class="form-input">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number *" required class="form-input">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" name="company" placeholder="Company Name" class="form-input">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select name="situation" required class="form-input form-select">
                                <option value="">What's your situation? *</option>
                                <option value="audit">Received IRS Audit Notice</option>
                                <option value="letter">Received IRS Letter/Request</option>
                                <option value="denial">ERC Claim Denied</option>
                                <option value="pending">Claim Still Pending</option>
                                <option value="proactive">Proactive Protection</option>
                                <option value="other">Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <textarea name="message" placeholder="Tell us about your situation (optional)" rows="4" class="form-input" style="resize: vertical;"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Submit Request &rarr;</button>
                    </form>
                    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 1rem;">100% confidential. No obligation. Response within 24 hours.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Info -->
            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Other Ways to Reach Us</h2>

                <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <div style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Call Us</h3>
                            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Speak directly with a team member</p>
                            <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none;">{{ site.phone }}</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <div style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Email Us</h3>
                            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">We respond within 24 hours</p>
                            <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none;">{{ site.email }}</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <div style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Business Hours</h3>
                            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST</p>
                            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">Weekend: By appointment</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Trust badges -->
                <div style="background: var(--bg-gray); border-radius: 4px; padding: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Why Trust Us</h3>
                    <ul style="list-style: none;">
                        <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--primary);">&#10003;</span>
                            <span>5 former IRS staff members</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--primary);">&#10003;</span>
                            <span>20+ years of IRS representation</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--primary);">&#10003;</span>
                            <span>$50M+ in claims defended</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--primary);">&#10003;</span>
                            <span>500+ businesses protected</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container-sm">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: 2rem;">Common Questions</h2>
        </div>

        <div>
            <details class="faq-item" open>
                <summary>What happens after I submit the form?<span>&#8595;</span></summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Within 24 hours, a member of our team will contact you to schedule a free, confidential consultation. We'll discuss your situation and provide an initial risk assessment.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>Is my information confidential?<span>&#8595;</span></summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. All information you share with us is treated as strictly confidential. We will never share your information without your explicit consent.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>Is there any cost for the initial consultation?<span>&#8595;</span></summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">No. The initial risk assessment and consultation are completely free with no obligation. We'll explain your options and you can decide if you'd like to proceed.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>Can you help if my original filer is gone?<span>&#8595;</span></summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes. Many of our clients came to us after their original ERC filer closed or became unresponsive. We can step in as your representative and work with whatever documentation is available.</p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
